The prestigious MrDodgy Invitational 2.0 is a 16-player knockout tournament taking place in the chess24 Playzone from 12-16 May 2021. Each match consists of 12 blitz games, with the first player to 6.5 points winning. The blitz games are played at a time control of 5 minutes for

all moves (no increment). If the players are tied at 6:6 they play a single Armageddon game, with the higher-rated player getting White. Official website: events.chess24.com/mrdodgy-invitational
